data.description: Location Location, Stunning 5 Beds 3 1/2 Baths conveniently located close to Hwy 6 and  Westpark Tollway; it is about midway between I10 and 59. This spacious home has many great features including 2 staircases! High ceiling The backyard is an oasis with a gazebo, many fruit trees & landscaping. Additional features include a first-floor master suite, a wood-burning fireplace, a huge game room with a built-in kitchen, and a detached 2-car garage.  It is zoned to Fort Bend ISD. Close to Sugar Land Town Square.
